  "text": "In this paper, the adopted SMPC for the AC system power control covers two parts, predicting and optimization. After predicting the future combined condition, the power control of AC system is optimized via DP at each predicted time step [CITATION_1] . In the SMPC formulation, state equipment can be formulated as { ̇= c + r + m + n − air air aiṙ == (4)",
